Subject: [PATCH] Fix PEP8 issues with latest pycodestyle (#6636)

---
 .pycodestyle                                              | 2 +-
 web/pgacloud/utils/misc.py                                | 2 +-
 web/pgadmin/authenticate/mfa/tests/test_mfa_view.py       | 2 +-
 web/pgadmin/authenticate/mfa/utils.py                     | 2 +-
 .../servers/databases/subscriptions/__init__.py           | 2 +-
